## File & Repo Hygiene

- `.gitignore` should be the first commit in any new repo
- Never commit API keys, secrets, or credentials — not even temporarily
- `README.md` required at repo root; keep it current
- `docs/` directory for design documents (BRIEF.md, SPEC.md, DECISIONS.md),
  following the template used in ~/coding/krashen
- Delete dead code rather than commenting it out; git history is the undo buffer

