## Project Documentation Conventions

All active projects maintain three documents in `docs/`:

- `BRIEF.md` — stable: what, why, for whom, hard constraints
- `SPEC.md` — living: feature-by-feature design
- `DECISIONS.md` — append-only: key architectural choices with rationale

Update DECISIONS.md any time a non-obvious architectural or design decision is made.
These docs are also attached to the corresponding Claude Project in claude.ai for
browser-based design conversations.

